summary: This is an FBI 302 form summarizing attempts by Special Agents to locate and interview Larry Visok on July 9-11, 2019. Agents contacted Visok at his residence in West Palm Beach, Florida, where he requested an attorney and was served with a Grand Jury subpoena.

persons.name: Larry Visok
persons.context: Agents attempted to interview him at his residence; he requested an attorney and was served with a Grand Jury subpoena.

events.title: FBI Attempts to Interview Larry Visok
events.description: FBI Special Agents made contact with Larry Visok at his residence in West Palm Beach, Florida. Visok requested an attorney and was provided with a Grand Jury subpoena.

events.title: FBI Investigation Period
events.description: FBI Special Agents were tasked with locating and attempting to interview Larry Visok over this three-day period.

locations: West Palm Beach, Florida, United States
keyFacts: FBI Special Agents attempted to interview Larry Visok between July 9 and July 11, 2019.
Visok was contacted at his residence in West Palm Beach, Florida.
Visok requested an attorney upon contact by the FBI.
Visok was served with a Grand Jury subpoena.
The document is an FBI 302 form dated July 16, 2019, summarizing the interview attempts.
